item.title: Day 5
item.description: I created simulations of circuits in Tinkercad and made a PowerPoint on it.

item.title: Day 4
item.description: I finished the replica of DFS in GatherTown and started working on a replica of Level 2 of Science Centre. I also tried a drone simulator and programmed a drone to do certain actions from an ipad.

item.title: Day 3
item.description: I started making a replica of DFS in GatherTown and made PowerPoints on making a GatherTown space, such as how to add custom objects into the space. I also worked on a PowerPoint on how to use FFMPEG to edit videos.

item.title: Day 2
item.description: I learnt how to use a laser cutter and made a few light boxes as tokens of appreciation for Science Centre competitions.

item.title: Day 1
item.description: I learnt how to create a website using Visual Studio Code, Githubm Gitbash etc.
